com.google.cloud.logging.testing

Class RemoteLoggingHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.cloud.logging.testing.RemoteLoggingHelper

  • public class RemoteLoggingHelper
extends Object
    Utility to create a remote logging configuration for testing. Logging options can be obtained via the getOptions() method. Returned options have custom ServiceOptions.getRetryParams(): RetryParams.getMaxRetryDelayMillis() is 30000, RetryParams.getTotalRetryPeriodMillis() is 120000 and RetryParams.getInitialRetryDelayMillis() is 250. GrpcServiceOptions.getInitialTimeout() is set to 60000, GrpcServiceOptions.getMaxTimeout() is set to 240000 and GrpcServiceOptions.getTimeoutMultiplier() is set to 1.5.
